  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >swim around as a fish and do tricks in the air</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you're a fish. you do tricks. that's the whole game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/74e5d8ff3781d2b1b0b14af9b51e64b8.poster.avif?t=1766322175\" width=350 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/74e5d8ff3781d2b1b0b14af9b51e64b8.webm?t=1766322175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >swim around underwater to build momentum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >launch yourself into the air</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >wiggle around to perform \"tricks\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >try not to question why a fish would do this</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/45b3dc7cc088eb867fca812cdc299312.poster.avif?t=1766322175\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/45b3dc7cc088eb867fca812cdc299312.webm?t=1766322175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/45b3dc7cc088eb867fca812cdc299312.mp4?t=1766322175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/72489e2d9737c08575c700191a7cbf3d.poster.avif?t=1766322175\" width=270 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521300/extras/72489e2d9737c08575c700191a7cbf3d.webm?t=1766322175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >different fish that all swim the same</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >various bodies of water that are functionally identical</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a scoring system that pretends fish acrobatics is a legitimate sport</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >grind rails</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >probably the best fish simulator ever made. also the worst.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DISCLAIMER: the game is short. It's more of a toy to play with while watching tv/listening to podcasts tbh</p>",
